2.2 Rover Fleet Composition (First Landing)

```
Vulcan-1 Mission Payload (25,000 kg total):
├── AWR-Mars Fleet (4 units @ 850 kg):     3,400 kg
├── ARC-Mars Fleet (2 units @ 1,200 kg):   2,400 kg  
├── ASR-Mars Fleet (2 units @ 1,500 kg):   3,000 kg
├── Foundry Core (10t capacity):           4,500 kg
