```

2.3 Communication & Coordination Network

```
AIADN (Artificial Intelligence Autonomous Deployed Network)
├── Layer 1: Rover-to-Rover Mesh (100 Mbps Ethernet, ≤1 km)
├── Layer 2: Base Server Coordination (1 Gbps fiber when docked)
├── Layer 3: Earth Oversight (1 Mbps via orbital relay, 4-24 min latency)
├── Layer 4: Emergency Beacon (S-band, 48-hour battery)
└── Learning: Federated AI updates every 3 sols
```

