\end{align*}

Appendix B: Derived Constants

1. Optimal walking frequency in 0.38g:

f_{opt} = \frac{1}{2\pi}\sqrt{\frac{g_M}{l_{leg}}} \approx 0.5\ \text{Hz} \quad \text{for} \ l_{leg} = 1.5\ \text{m}

1. Regolith excavation energy:

E_{dig} = 0.15\ \text{kWh/m}^3 \quad \text{(at 0.38g, cohesive soil)}

1. Sulfur concrete curing time:

t_{cure} = 2\ \text{hours} \cdot e^{(T-130)/15} \quad T \ \text{in} \ ^\circ\text{C}

